00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:43,260
That's a perfectly good law.

686
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:47,360
We talked about the concept,

687
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:49,940
the same concept in the context of a die

688
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:50,880
with six faces,

689
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:53,120
