00:28:01,940 --> 00:28:02,720
Could be any state.

777
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:06,040
It's not the same after a certain time

778
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:07,120
as it was to begin with,

779
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:09,560
but we're following one specific state

780
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:11,000
of a system that's been prepared

781
00:28:11,450 --> 00:28:13,020
and then allowed to evolve

782
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:15,880
by whatever means things evolve.

783
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:17,380
Alright,

784
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:19,820
the postulate is

785
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:21,580
that psi of t

786
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:24,020
can be obtained

787
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:28,040
from psi of zero,

788
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:31,160
this means time zero,

789
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:35,240
by an operation on psi of zero.

790
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:36,420
A unique,

791
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,760
definite operation

792
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:40,960
which is governed by the laws,

793
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:42,720
