794
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,740
for that system.

795
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,600
So we have to do something to the vector.

796
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:50,100
It doesn't stay the same.

797
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:53,100
So let's represent what we do

798
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:58,880
