799
00:29:00,180 --> 00:29:01,380
Now incidentally,

800
00:29:01,380 --> 00:29:04,180
we didn't have to start with time zero.

801
00:29:04,300 --> 00:29:05,560
We could have started with time

802
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:06,900
something else.

803
00:29:08,959 --> 00:29:09,620
So,

804
00:29:09,620 --> 00:29:11,420
we can say that

805
00:29:11,420 --> 00:29:11,440
psi of t

