00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:07,760
Or you might have the hypothesis

834
00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:09,080
that U is an operation

835
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:10,520
but not a linear operator,

836
00:30:10,880 --> 00:30:12,280
some other kind of operation.

837
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:13,920
You can try it.

838
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,100
You'll very shortly run into big troubles

839
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:17,380
