840
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:18,880
It's been tried,

841
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:19,700
I guarantee you.

842
00:30:19,780 --> 00:30:21,340
It's been tried and repeatedly,

843
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:22,480
every so often,

844
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:25,980
some physicist will try to invent something

845
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:27,760
and then some other person will come along

846
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:28,180
and say,

847
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:28,440
look,

848
00:30:28,560 --> 00:30:31,720
that has troubles with locality

