00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:35,940
It's a very complex interpretation.

852
00:30:37,120 --> 00:30:38,920
And you're free to try.

853
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:40,220
I've given up trying.

854
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:43,180
I actually never tried.

855
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:48,480
Right,

