00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:27,140
Then,

872
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,620
if phi,

873
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:30,820
to begin with,

874
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,840
is orthogonal to psi,

